column2: SELECT TOP #  p.ra, p.dec, p.petroMag_u, p.petroMag_g, p.petroMag_r, p.petroMag_i, p.petroMag_z,  p.petroMagErr_u, p.petroMagErr_g, petroMagErr_r, p.petroMagErr_i, p.petroMagErr_z,  s.class, s.z as redshift FROM PhotoObj AS p  JOIN SpecObj AS s ON s.bestobjid = p.objid   JOIN galSpecLine AS g ON g.specObjID = p.objid  WHERE   s.class=&&&
